{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8a8eb57fd5","title":"毛泽东在刘少奇作反修报告时的插话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"27f3aa0eef","index":0,"year":1964,"month":9,"day":4,"articleId":"8a8eb57fd5"}],"tags":[{"id":"3aaab89c2a","name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4362e22264","type":"title","text":"在刘少奇作反修报告时的插话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a8eb57fd5"},{"id":"d1fcfa00a4","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：蛇是引出来好打，还是钻黑洞里好打？","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a8eb57fd5"},{"id":"421de7f8ba","type":"paragraph","text":"刘：对苏斯洛夫报告我们赞成发表，它不发。出了八评后引出来了。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a8eb57fd5"},{"id":"5c32338b6c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：一九五六年以来，苏联骂斯大林，我们一论、二论发表后，他就失去了主动权。点名不光我们两家，东欧也点名了。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a8eb57fd5"},{"id":"3aff547cd2","type":"paragraph","text":"刘：苏联批评罗自力更生，罗回击，用我们评苏联的话。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a8eb57fd5"},{"id":"6f5d7b8015","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：不是内部的事，正在电台上干，公开干了。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a8eb57fd5"},{"id":"f8b8d383ee","type":"paragraph","text":"控制、反控制的冲突，第一位的不是中国，而是东欧国家。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a8eb57fd5"},{"id":"213f3dddbc","type":"paragraph","text":"刘：罗已做了苏断绝经济关系的准备，自己不能制造武器，要求我国去人到罗访问，不讲话都可以使人震惊，去了不讲话，握握手都很重要。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a8eb57fd5"},{"id":"a94837b62d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：中苏关系准备两手，准备破裂，争取拖。哪天出事，不要出于意料之外，天下大事，合久必分，分久必合。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a8eb57fd5"},{"id":"2bc89879fd","type":"paragraph","text":"刘：巴西老党四万人，成立新党六千人。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a8eb57fd5"},{"id":"2f931a370f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：是四万人可靠，还是六千人可靠？","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a8eb57fd5"},{"id":"454b3cbdea","type":"paragraph","text":"南昌暴动轰轰烈烈，剩下不多人，以后发展了三十万人，长征剩下几万人，以后发展起来，山不在高。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a8eb57fd5"},{"id":"24bcec1dfb","type":"paragraph","text":"有了修正主义，列宁主义才能万岁！","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a8eb57fd5"},{"id":"99b846dbd9","type":"paragraph","text":"不注意一定出修正主义，注意可能出可能不出；准备出，可能不出。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a8eb57fd5"}],"page":{"id":"aadb599ce6","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a8eb57fd5","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}